This guide outlines the construction of a production-ready **Digital Guestbook**. We will build a full-stack application that allows visitors to leave messages and provides a secure dashboard for you to moderate them.

### The Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice | Why? |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Framework** | **Next.js 14+ (App Router)** | Provides a unified full-stack environment with React. Server Components and Server Actions simplify data fetching and mutations without needing a separate Express API. |
| **Styling** | **Tailwind CSS + Shadcn UI** | Tailwind allows for rapid, consistent styling. Shadcn/UI provides accessible, high-quality components (inputs, cards, buttons) out of the box. |
| **Database** | **PostgreSQL (via Supabase)** | A relational database is ideal for structured data like messages. Supabase offers a generous free tier and easy management. |
