#### C. Content Protection (Subscription Gating)
Using Supabase Row Level Security (RLS) is the production way to handle this. You don't just hide it in the UI; you block it at the database level.

```sql
-- Only allow access to premium posts if the user has an 'active' subscription
CREATE POLICY "Premium content access" ON posts
  FOR SELECT
  USING (
    is_premium = false OR 
    EXISTS (
      SELECT 1 FROM subscriptions 
      WHERE user_id = auth.uid() AND status = 'active'
    )
  );
```

