| **Backend** | **NestJS (Node.js)** | Provides excellent Dependency Injection, making it easy to "inject" a tenant-specific database client into services. |
| **Database** | **PostgreSQL** | Best-in-class support for `SCHEMAS` and Row Level Security (RLS). |
| **ORM** | **Prisma** | High-type safety. We will use it with a dynamic connection factory to switch schemas on the fly. |
| **Frontend** | **Next.js** | Industry standard for SaaS. Supports middleware for tenant sub-domain routing (e.g., `apple.saas.com`). |
| **Auth** | **Clerk** | Handles "Organizations" out of the box, simplifying the mapping of users to tenants. |

