### 1. Database Schema (`prisma/schema.prisma`)
This schema handles users, roles, and the relational nature of quizzes.

```prisma
datasource db {
  provider = "postgresql"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
}

enum Role {
  TEACHER
  STUDENT
}

model User {
  id          String       @id @default(cuid())
  email       String       @unique
  role        Role         @default(STUDENT)
