### 2. Dynamic Form Builder Logic

To allow schools to create custom questions, we define a JSON structure for the `Form.config` field.

**Example Configuration:**
```json
[
  { "id": "q1", "type": "text", "label": "Student Name", "required": true },
  { "id": "q2", "type": "select", "label": "Grade Level", "options": ["K", "1", "2"] },
  { "id": "q3", "type": "checkbox", "label": "I agree to the terms", "required": true }
