We need to track the relationship between users, their registries, and the items within.

```prisma
datasource db {
  provider = "postgresql"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
}

model Registry {
  id          String   @id @default(cuid())
  userId      String   // From Clerk
  title       String
  description String?
  slug        String   @unique
