### 1. The Database Schema & Logic

We need to store events with a `GEOGRAPHY` point and an array of tags.

```sql
CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS postgis;

CREATE TABLE events (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  title TEXT NOT NULL,
  location GEOGRAPHY(POINT, 4326) NOT NULL,
  check_in_count INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
