### 2. The Ranking Algorithm (The "Single Query")

To compute the score in one pass, we use this formula:
$$Score = (W_{geo} \times \frac{1}{1 + dist}) + (W_{social} \times \log(checkins + 1)) + (W_{interest} \times |UserTags \cap EventTags|)$$

We will implement this in the SQL query below.

